Titolo: Rex Nebular and the Cosmic Gender Bender

Anno: 1992

Descrizione: Rex Nebular and the Cosmic Gender Bender is a point-and-click graphic adventure game developed and published by MicroProse in November of 1992. The game is the first graphical adventure game developed by MicroProse, Return of the Phantom and Dragonsphere being the other ones. It was developed using the MicroProse Adventure Development system, and made use of 256-colour graphics. Tommo purchased the rights to this game and digitally publishes it through its Retroism brand in 2015.

